<div class="courseblock main">
<p class="courseblocktitle"><strong>CHDV&#160;25750.  The Psychology and Neurobiology of Stress.  100 Units.</strong></p><p class="courseblockdesc">
This course explores the topic of stress and its influence on behavior and neurobiology. Specifically, the course will discuss how factors such as age, gender, and social context interact to influence how we respond to stressors both physiologically and behaviorally. The course will also explore how stress influences mental and physical health.</p><p class="courseblockdetail">
